claim.claim-text:
A composition for producing an absorbable polylactone copolymer comprising:
a.) about 2 mole percent to about 80 mole percent a first lactone monomer
comprising glycolide;b.) from about 98 to about 20 mole percent of a second lactone monomer other than
glycolide;c.) a monofunctional initiator; andd.) a di-functional initiator;
wherein the molar ratio of mono-functional to di-functional initiator is from about
10:90 to about 90:10;
